Kurasa kau ceroboh.

1497
02:00:01,166 --> 02:00:03,166
Kau tahu semua sejak awal.

1498
02:00:06,916 --> 02:00:09,250
- Terima kasih, Zeta. Sungguh.
- Elena.

1499
02:00:09,750 --> 02:00:10,750
Aku datang.

1500
02:00:33,583 --> 02:00:35,083
