Ibu.

1502
02:00:40,541 --> 02:00:42,666
Hei. Bicaralah kepadaku.

1503
02:00:43,583 --> 02:00:45,291
Bicaralah kepadaku.

1504
02:00:52,625 --> 02:00:55,541
Sudah berakhir.

1505
02:00:58,541 --> 02:00:59,625
Sudah berakhir.

