02:01:01,166 --> 02:01:02,041
Sudah berakhir.

1507
02:01:42,250 --> 02:01:43,750
<i>Ada kartu pos...</i>

1508
02:01:45,458 --> 02:01:48,083
<i>Beberapa tempat mengagumkan
yang kudatangi.</i>

1509
02:01:57,250 --> 02:02:00,250
