1510
02:02:04,000 --> 02:02:04,916
<i>Anakku sayang,</i>

1511
02:02:05,750 --> 02:02:09,416
{\an8}<i>jika kau baca surat ini,
artinya aku sudah tak bersamamu lagi.</i>

